  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive starship customisation option, creating a unique well-worn appearance for <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Fighter</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Hauler</span> class starships.<br><br>Acquire starship components by breaking down existing ships at the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Starship Outfitting</span> unit aboard any space station. Visit the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Starship Fabricator</span> to design and assemble a new vessel.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一份专属飞船自定义选项，能够为你的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">战斗机</span>与<span class=\"name name-stellar\">拖运船</span>级飞船带来独特的磨损外观。<br><br>在任意空间站的<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船装备装置</span>分解现有飞船以获取飞船构件。拜访<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船制造机</span>以设计并组装新的飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的太空船客製化選項，為<span class=\"name name-stellar\">戰鬥機</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">拖運船</span>級太空船打造獨特的破舊外觀。<br><br>在任何太空站的<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船改造</span>單位分解現有的太空船，取得太空船元件。前往<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船製造器</span>，設計並組裝新太空船。"
  },
